review_blob: Coffee, roasty. Doesnt hint at coffee, it is coffee flavoured! As coffee beers go its not bad some are over the top. Very sweet, wouldnt want to drink more than one at a time. Bottle from Stirchley Wines, Birmingham.
Bottle from Bernies Real Ale Off Licence. Tastes stronger than it is Orange, caramel. Definitely have again. Nice BBB story.
